author: nspiegelberg
msg: [master] Fix TestHeapSize broken by adding favored nodes to HRegion
Summary: The favored nodes field in the HRegion was not counted in the heap
size. Marking as private because the favored node code does not have JIRAs yet,
or is considered a master-only feature, as far as I know.

author: sebb
msg: A circularity was detected in the static initializers of the two classes
referenced by the bug instance.  Many kinds of unexpected behavior may
This was caused by calling the static method SampleResult.sampleNsClock() from a NanoOffset static block; fixed by performing the init externally.
